-- Accessories
(4,	'ARMIT',	'ARMIT.jpg',	1617.00,	'Armit: There is nothing empressive about Armit except the results. Armit is not a skill simulator; it has only one objective, strength. Using RepMotions strength protocol, Armit provides skiers with an effective way to strengthen their poling muscles with three functional exercises and efficient elastic resistance.'),
(4,	'BECOMING A BETTER SKIER DVD', NULL, 639.00, 'This is an instructional video that covers both traditional classic skiing and skating. The video has numerous drills to improve balance and stability. The Instructor is Zach Caldwell who has worked with many members of the US ski team. The instructional program was developed by Zach during the five years he was program director for the New England Nordic Ski Association. This video is both for beginners as well as elite skiers. Emphasis is on proper body position, core strength, balance and stability.'),
(4,	'DIAMOND STONE', 'Diamond_Stone.jpg', 792.00, 'This inexpensive tool is the best hand tool we have found for sharpening carbide tips. To roller ski on asphalt it is very important to have sharp carbide tips. It’s a good idea to quickly sharpen your tips before each outing as sharp tips make for a more pleasant experience and dull, worn down tips are harder to sharpen.'),
(4, 'F125 - FENDER', 'F150.jpg',	396.00,	'The V2 Fenders are designed for use on the rear wheel and only cover the top and rear of the wheel so a brake can still be used.'),
(4,	'F98 - FENDER',  'F98.jpg',		396.00,	'The V2 Fenders are designed for use on the rear wheel and only cover the top and rear of the wheel so a brake can still be used.'),
(4, 'HIGH PRESSURE PUMP',	'pump.jpg', 1419.00,	'This shock pump is an essential item for keeping the tires properly inflated on all Aero models. Because of the small size of the Aero wheels the valve stem can be difficult to access with most bicycle pumps but this pump easily threads on.'),
(4, 'OMNI PREP',	'Omni_Prep.jpg',	5.00,		'Omni Prep is a polishing material that shears the microscopic polyethylene hairs and polishes better than other materials. Skis polished with Omni Prep have no hairs, while skis polished with fibertex produce thousands of fine hairs, which are only visible with a good light source and a very high magnification. Ski tuning guru Zach Caldwell said there is nothing like Omni Prep for final polishing.'),
(4,	'SKI POLES',	'vasa_poles.jpg',	2607.00,	'Vasa Racing: Only 58 grams per meter. A 160 cm Vasa is lighter than a C1 pole. Stiff and strong with a very low swing weight. Made from high modulus carbon graphite with a very small percentage of high strength carbon to give the poles better durabitlity.The Vasa is available in sizes 130 cm to 167.2 cm in 2.5 cm increments. Available as shafts only or as complete poles which come with cork grips and an effecient competition strap and your choice of roller ski ferrules or snow baskets. A great pole at a great price.'),

--Nordixc
(5, 'NXL125RC',	'NXL125RC.jpg',	16467.00,		'The NXL125RC is based on our XL125RC roller ski with two 125mm pneumatic wheels in the back and a 150mm one way clutch wheel in the front making it very easy to balance on. The pneumatic wheels make it ideal for hard packed dirt roads and bike paths and are exceptionally smooth on pavement. The large pneumatic wheels combined with the stable three-wheeled platform make it an ideal choice for beginning classic skiers. Includes speed reducer, a brake, and the Becoming a Better Skier DVD'),
(5,	'NXL98RC',	'NXL98RC.jpg',	16467.00,		'The NXL98RC is based on our XL98RC three-wheeled classic ski designed for good pavement. In the front we use a 100mm split-rim clutch wheel and in the back we use the same durable 100mm free wheels as our XL98R and XL98SL. Another benefit is that the narrow front wheel is less likely to stop dead when encountering debris in the road. Includes speed reducer, a brake, and the Becoming a Better Skier DVD')

